		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 279.33333333333px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 277.33333333333px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Basilica of St Josaphat, Milwaukee, United States"><img alt="Basilica of St Josaphat, Milwaukee, United States" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg/416px-Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg" decoding="async" width="278" height="185" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg/624px-Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg/831px-Basilica_of_St._Josaphat.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1200" data-file-height="800" /></a></span></div>
