		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 220px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 218px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="The Church of St Nicola, Kungur, Russia, has an apse and wide ambulatory."><img alt="The Church of St Nicola, Kungur, Russia, has an apse and wide ambulatory." src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg/327px-Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg" decoding="async" width="218" height="220" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg/490px-Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg/653px-Kungur_nicola01_cropped.jpg 2x" data-file-width="2057" data-file-height="2078" /></a></span></div>
