			<div class="thumb" style="width: 147.33333333333px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Ambo for reading the Gospel at Sant&#39;Apollinare Nuovo, Ravenna"><img alt="Ambo for reading the Gospel at Sant&#39;Apollinare Nuovo, Ravenna" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg/221px-Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg" decoding="async" width="148" height="220" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg/331px-Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg/442px-Pulpit_-_Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo_-_Ravenna_2016.jpg 2x" data-file-width="3457" data-file-height="5160" /></a></span></div>
			<div class="gallerytext"><a href="/wiki/Ambon_(liturgy)" title="Ambon (liturgy)">Ambo</a> for reading the <a href="/wiki/Gospel" title="Gospel">Gospel</a> at <a href="/wiki/Sant%27Apollinare_Nuovo" class="mw-redirect" title="Sant&#39;Apollinare Nuovo">Sant'Apollinare Nuovo</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ravenna" title="Ravenna">Ravenna</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 150px">
