		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 172px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 170px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="St. Paul&#39;s Cathedral, Mdina (1696–1705)"><img alt="St. Paul&#39;s Cathedral, Mdina (1696–1705)" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg/255px-St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg" decoding="async" width="170" height="220" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg/382px-St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/87/St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg/510px-St_Paul%27s_Cathedral_Mdina.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1668" data-file-height="2160" /></a></span></div>
