<h3><span id="Architectural_styles_.28chronological_order.29"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Architectural_styles_(chronological_order)">Architectural styles (chronological order)</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Architecture_of_cathedrals_and_great_churches&amp;action=edit&amp;section=42" title="Edit section: Architectural styles (chronological order)"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Early_Christian_art_and_architecture" title="Early Christian art and architecture">Early Christian art and architecture</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Byzantine_architecture" title="Byzantine architecture">Byzantine architecture</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Eastern_Orthodox_church_architecture" title="Eastern Orthodox church architecture">Eastern Orthodox church architecture</a></li>
